    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you are so cool, that even ice shivers in your presence. When you cast a ninjutsu that requires concentration, you may change the casting time to a bonus action and reduce the concentration cost to 0. You also gain advantage on concentration checks and you cannot gain any penalties on making these checks. You can enhance a ninjutsu in this way twice per rest.</p>",
